                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           
                           <note> Written in the same hand (?) as Additio 1; possibly its
                              continuation or as writing exersice. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1"><desc>- Corrections (letters or words) written interlineally:
                           e.g., <locus target="#1ra">1ra</locus>, 4rb, 5ra, 40ra, 41vb, 44ra.</desc></item>
